Summary: I saw a green light orb over the gulf state park fishing pier in gulf shores,al It looked like it was falling into the ocean and then burn out. It took about 5 seconds.
divs: Sighting DetailsI was fishing at the gulf state park pier around 7:30 pm on Sunday September 25th and I saw a green fireball streak across the sky-I thought maybe it was a small aircraft and was going to fall into the ocean, but before it got to the water it just burnt out. I probably watched it for about 5 seconds. I was wondering if anyone else saw it.
trends: There have been 6 other sightings in Gulf Shores
There were no other sightings in Gulf Shores on or around September 25th 2011
